Package voldemort.server.protocol

The server side of request RPC handling.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
RequestHandler A request handler that answers client requests in some given format
RequestHandlerFactory A factory that gets the appropriate request handler for a given RequestFormatType.
StreamRequestHandler Implements an iterator-esque streaming request handler wherein we keep executing handleRequest until it returns StreamRequestHandler.StreamRequestHandlerState.COMPLETE.
 

Class Summary
AbstractRequestHandler A base class with a few helper fields for writing a RequestHandler
SocketRequestHandlerFactory A factory that gets the appropriate request handler for a given RequestFormatType.
